      <hr />
      <h3>‚öôÔ∏è  Drivetrain</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Rear derailleur:</strong> SRAM X01 Eagle</li>
        <li><strong>Crank:</strong> SRAM X1</li>
        <li><strong>Cassette:</strong> SRAM GX Eagle</li>
